SUMMARY:"A Sheep From Another Fold"- Spiritual Video Night
DESCRIPTION:Roanoke Spiritual Experiences Group\n**Description:**\nCome join us for a 30-minute video of timeless wisdom from Harold Klemp’s talk\, **“A Sheep From Another Fold.**” Uplifting and insightful\, his talks can help you unravel some of the perplexing mysteries of life. Each showing will be followed by group discussion\; a time to share your own experiences and nagging questions about life’s many challenges.\nSponsored by ECKANKAR\, the Path of Spiritual Freedom.\nPlease register in advance for this meeting at:\n[https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/DZQK4PUeSBmaxdeqEy_Hjw](https://us06web.zoom.us/meeting/register/DZQK4PUeSBmaxdeqEy_Hjw)\nAfter registering\, you will receive a confirmation email containing login information for joining the meeting.\nINTERNATIONAL GUESTS\, PLEASE NOTE: This event is not intended for anyone who is barred by the laws of their country from attending. Please follow the laws of your home country.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/roanoke-spiritual-experiences-group/events/313553451/
